summary: A new character save i made where you start off in a camp.
descriptionHtml:
You awake to see your brother lying in a pool of his own blood, all that you have is your hide armor and you trusty iron sword. 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is an alternative beginning i made. it is only basic and i will be working on it. there are no quests and i think that helgen is destroyed.

please test this out and if you like it leave a comment and tell me whats good and what could be improved
author: DeathGrizzle
